org.gephi.attribute.api

Class AttributeUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gephi.attribute.api.AttributeUtils

  • public class AttributeUtils
extends Object
    Attribute utilities.

    The attribute system is built with a set of supported column types. This class contains utilities to parse and convert supported types. It also contains utilities to manipulate primitive arrays (the preferred array type) and date/time types.
